= INSTALL MAVEN - - -
https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
- both the top tar.gz (prefer) and bin.zip has same content take any.
- extract to a_2 dir add bin to PATH var in .bash_profile (my base) or .bashrc (can create a_2 seperate MVNBIN env var)
export M2_HOME=/Users/vn0sawo/dev/apache-maven-3.6.3 # was 3.6.1
